arts.ttl: Hibs move third in Premiership with victory against Aberdeen
arts.sum: Thibault Klidje and Elie Youan were on target as high-flying Hibernian held on to claim a 2-1 Premiership victory away to Aberdeen.

arts.ttl: Mats Knoester delivers brutal Aberdeen verdict on AEK Athens mauling and warns we must 'get over it' for Hibs
arts.sum: The Dutch defender wasn't pulling any punches on why Jimmy Thelin's team got it wrong in Greece
